SQL> SELECT phone, COUNT(*)

  3  GROUP BY phone
  4  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;

PHONE                       COUNT(*)                                                                                                                                                                    
------------------------- ----------                                                                                                                                                                    
7894561230                         2
